column4: "Waltse For Dave. Chick Corea. from the 'Friends' Album. (Dedicated to Dave Brubeck) Lead sheet is in 'The New Real Book' Vol 2 (Sher Music) page 407. The original is played on Flute - I have changed this to Harmonica because my flute sound is less than c\012"
"'Waltse for Dave' by Chick Corea. dedicated to Dave Brubeck"
"Harmonica solo - on original recording was Joe Farrell playing Flute"
